<details>

  <summary>A problem? Click here to find a solution.</summary>

  ### Getting specific information

  Type `/help send message` in the "[Converse](https://singularicula.me/?tab=chat)" tab to get more information on how to send a message.

  Once you have energy and can send messages, you could type somthing like `/help energy earn` to get more information on how to earn energy.

  If you still have questions, you can then ask them in the chat and the model you picked will do its best to help you.

  ### Asking for help

  If you still are having trouble, you can visit our [Dicussion Room](https://github.com/orgs/PredictiveSingularity/discussions). The [_Q&A_](https://github.com/orgs/PredictiveSingularity/discussions/categories/q-a) section is a great place to ask questions and get help as we'll pin most voted questions to the top.

  ### Opening a ticket

  If you still can't find a solution, checkout [currently open](https://github.com/PredictiveSingularity/Chat-Interface/issues) ([and closed](https://github.com/PredictiveSingularity/Chat-Interface/issues?q=is%3Aissue)) tickets, maybe it's a known issue and this would be the place to get more information about it.
  
  If you fail to find a ticket about your specific issue, you can [open a new one](https://github.com/PredictiveSingularity/Chat-Interface/issues).

</details>